orkflows/main.yml` 含 `main` 和 `release-*`; `grep 'make docker-build' .github/workflows/main.yml` 有输出; `grep 'setup-buildx-action' .github/workflows/main.yml` 有输出\n32: \n33: ---\n34: \n35: ### T-003: lint.yml — Go Lint (path-filtered)\n36: \n37: - [ ] T-003.01 Create `.github/workflows/lint.yml` with `name: Lint`\n38: - [ ] T-003.02 Trigger: `pull_request` with branches `main`, `release-*`\n39: - [ ] T-003.03 Define `dorny/paths-filter@v3` step with filter `lint`: `**/*.go`, `go.mod`, `go.sum`, `.golangci.yml`, `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n40: - [ ] T-003.04 Job `golangci` on `ubuntu-latest`: step 1 — `actions/checkout@v4`\n41: - [ ] T-003.05 Job `golangci`: step 2 — paths-filter step with id `filter`\n42: - [ ] T-003.06 Job `golangci`: step 3 — `actions/setup-go@v5` with `go-version: '1.24'`, conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.lint == 'true'`\n43: - [ ] T-003.07 Job `golangci`: step 4 — `run: make lint`, conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.lint == 'true'`\n44: \n45: **验收**: `yq '.name' .github/workflows/lint.yml` → `Lint`; `grep 'dorny/paths-filter' .github/workflows/lint.yml` 有输出; `grep 'go-version.*1.24' .github/workflows/lint.yml` 有输出; `grep 'make lint' .github/workflows/lint.yml` 有输出; `grep \"steps.filter.outputs.lint == 'true'\" .github/workflows/lint.yml` 出现 ≥ 2 次\n46: \n47: ---\n48: \n49: ### T-004: test-coverage.yml — Test Coverage (with Codecov upload)\n50: \n51: - [ ] T-004.01 Create `.github/workflows/test-coverage.yml` with `name: Test Coverage`\n52: - [ ] T-004.02 Trigger: `pull_request` (branches: `main`), `merge_group`, `workflow_call` (secrets: `CODECOV_TOKEN` required: false)\n53: - [ ] T-004.03 Define `dorny/paths-filter@v3` step with filter `coverage`: `**`, `!*.md`, `!*.svg`, `!*.png`\n54: - [ ] T-004.04 Job `coverage` on `ubuntu-latest`: step 1 — `actions/checkout@v4`\n55: - [ ] T-004.05 Job `coverage`: step 2 — paths-filter step with id `filter`\n56: - [ ] T-004.06 Job `coverage`: step 3 — free-disk-space step (e.g. `jlumbroso/free-disk-space@v1.3.1` or equivalent), conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.coverage == 'true'`\n57: - [ ] T-004.07 Job `coverage`: step 4 — `actions/setup-go@v5` with `go-version: '1.24'`, conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.coverage == 'true'`\n58: - [ ] T-004.08 Job `coverage`: step 5 — `run: go test -race -v -coverprofile=coverage.out -coverpkg=./pkg/... ./pkg/...`, conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.coverage == 'true'`\n59: - [ ] T-004.09 Job `coverage`: step 6 — upload `coverage.out` as artifact (e.g. `actions/upload-artifact@v4`), conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.coverage == 'true'`\n60: - [ ] T-004.10 Job `coverage`: step 7 — `codecov/codecov-action@v5` with `token: ${{ secrets.CODECOV_TOKEN }}`, conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.coverage == 'true' && secrets.CODECOV_TOKEN != ''`\n61: \n62: **验收**: `yq '.name' .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml` → `Test Coverage`; `grep 'workflow_call' .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml` 有输出; `grep 'CODECOV_TOKEN' .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml` 出现 ≥ 2 次; `grep 'go test.*-race.*-coverprofile' .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml` 有输出; `grep 'free-disk-space' .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml` 有输出; `grep 'codecov-action' .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml` 有输出; `grep 'upload-artifact' .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml` 有输出\n63: \n64: ---\n65: \n66: ### T-005: e2e.yml — E2E Tests on Kind\n67: \n68: - [ ] T-005.01 Create `.github/workflows/e2e.yml` with `name: Agentcube E2E Tests`\n69: - [ ] T-005.02 Trigger: `pull_request` with branches `main`, `release-*`\n70: - [ ] T-005.03 Job `e2e-test` on `ubuntu-24.04` (or larger runner): step 1 — `actions/checkout@v4`\n71: - [ ] T-005.04 Job `e2e-test`: step 2 — `actions/setup-go@v5` with `go-version: '1.23'`\n72: - [ ] T-005.05 Job `e2e-test`: step 3 — `helm/kind-action@v1` with `install_only: true`, `cluster_name: agentcube-e2e`, `version: v0.30.0`\n73: - [ ] T-005.06 Job `e2e-test`: step 4 — `run: export ARTIFACTS_PATH=${{ github.workspace }}/e2e-logs`\n74: - [ ] T-005.07 Job `e2e-test`: step 5 — `run: make e2e`, id `e2e`\n75: - [ ] T-005.08 Job `e2e-test`: step 6 — upload `e2e-logs/` as artifact on failure, conditional `if: failure()`\n76: - [ ] T-005.09 Job `e2e-test`: step 7 — `run: make e2e-clean`, conditional `if: always()`\n77: \n78: **验收**: `yq '.name' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` → `Agentcube E2E Tests`; `grep 'ubuntu-24.04' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` 有输出; `grep 'go-version.*1.23' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` 有输出; `grep 'kind-action' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` 有输出; `grep 'install_only.*true' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` 有输出; `grep 'ARTIFACTS_PATH' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` 有输出; `grep 'make e2e' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` 有输出; `grep 'make e2e-clean' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` 有输出; `grep 'if: failure()' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` 有输出; `grep 'if: always()' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` 有输出\n79: \n80: ---\n81: \n82: ## Phase 2: Code Quality Workflows\n83: \n84: ### T-006: codegen-check.yml — Code Generation Drift Detection\n85: \n86: - [ ] T-006.01 Create `.github/workflows/codegen-check.yml` with `name: Codegen Check`\n87: - [ ] T-006.02 Trigger: `pull_request` with branches `main`, `release-*`\n88: - [ ] T-006.03 Define `dorny/paths-filter@v3` step with filter `codegen`: `pkg/apis/**`, `hack/**`, `.github/workflows/**`, `Makefile`\n89: - [ ] T-006.04 Job `codegen-check` on `ubuntu-latest`: step 1 — `actions/checkout@v4`\n90: - [ ] T-006.05 Job `codegen-check`: step 2 — paths-filter step with id `filter`\n91: - [ ] T-006.06 Job `codegen-check`: step 3 — `actions/setup-go@v5` with `go-version: '1.24.4'`, conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.codegen == 'true'`\n92: - [ ] T-006.07 Job `codegen-check`: step 4 — `run: make gen-check`, conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.codegen == 'true'`\n93: \n94: **验收**: `yq '.name' .github/workflows/codegen-check.yml` → `Codegen Check`; `grep 'go-version.*1.24.4' .github/workflows/codegen-check.yml` 有输出; `grep 'make gen-check' .github/workflows/codegen-check.yml` 有输出; `grep 'pkg/apis' .github/workflows/codegen-check.yml` 有输出; `grep 'hack/' .github/workflows/codegen-check.yml` 有输出\n95: \n96: ---\n97: \n98: ### T-007: copyright-check.yml — Copyright Header Verification\n99: \n100: - [ ] T-007.01 Create `.github/workflows/copyright-check.yml` with `name: Copyright Check`\n101: - [ ] T-007.02 Trigger: `pull_request` with branches `main`, `release-*`\n102: - [ ] T-007.03 Define `dorny/paths-filter@v3` step with filter `copyright`: `**`, `!*.md`, `!*.svg`, `!*.png`, `!docs/**`, `!.github/**`\n103: - [ ] T-007.04 Job `build` on `ubuntu-latest`: step 1 — `actions/checkout@v4`\n104: - [ ] T-007.05 Job `build`: step 2 — paths-filter step with id `filter`\n105: - [ ] T-007.06 Job `build`: step 3 — `run: sudo apt-get install -y moreutils`, conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.copyright == 'true'`\n106: - [ ] T-007.07 Job `build`: step 4 — `run: make gen-copyright`, conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.copyright == 'true'`\n107: - [ ] T-007.08 Job `build`: step 5 — `run: git diff --exit-code`, conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.copyright == 'true'`\n108: \n109: **验收**: `yq '.name' .github/workflows/copyright-check.yml` → `Copyright Check`; `grep 'moreutils' .github/workflows/copyright-check.yml` 有输出; `grep 'make gen-copyright' .github/workflows/copyright-check.yml` 有输出; `grep 'git diff --exit-code' .github/workflows/copyright-check.yml` 有输出; `grep '!docs/' .github/workflows/copyright-check.yml` 有输出; `grep '!.github/' .github/workflows/copyright-check.yml` 有输出\n110: \n111: ---\n112: \n113: ### T-008: codespell.yml — Spelling Check\n114: \n115: - [ ] T-008.01 Create `.github/workflows/codespell.yml` with `name: Codespell`\n116: - [ ] T-008.02 Trigger: `pull_request` with branches `main`, `release-*`\n117: - [ ] T-008.03 Job `codespell` on `ubuntu-latest`: step 1 — `actions/checkout@v4`\n118: - [ ] T-008.04 Job `codespell`: step 2 — backup/remove false-positive files (`pyproject.toml`, `package.json`, `package-lock.json` from root and nested), id `pre-check`\n119: - [ ] T-008.05 Job `codespell`: step 3 — `run: pip install codespell`\n120: - [ ] T-008.06 Job `codespell`: step 4 — `run: codespell --check-filenames --skip=<patterns> --ignore-words-list fo,nam,te,notin,NotIn .`\n121: - [ ] T-008.07 Job `codespell`: step 5 — restore backed-up files, conditional `if: always()`\n122: \n123: **验收**: `yq '.name' .github/workflows/codespell.yml` → `Codespell`; `grep 'codespell' .github/workflows/codespell.yml` 出现 ≥ 3 次; `grep 'pyproject.toml' .github/workflows/codespell.yml` 有输出; `grep 'package.json' .github/workflows/codespell.yml` 有输出; `grep 'package-lock.json' .github/workflows/codespell.yml` 有输出; `grep 'ignore-words-list' .github/workflows/codespell.yml` 有输出; `grep 'fo,nam,te,notin,NotIn' .github/workflows/codespell.yml` 有输出; `grep 'if: always()' .github/workflows/codespell.yml` 有输出\n124: \n125: ---\n126: \n127: ## Phase 3: Python Workflows\n128: \n129: ### T-009: python-sdk-tests.yml — Python SDK Unit Tests\n130: \n131: - [ ] T-009.01 Create `.github/workflows/python-sdk-tests.yml` with `name: Python SDK Tests`\n132: - [ ] T-009.02 Trigger: `pull_request`, `merge_group`\n133: - [ ] T-009.03 Define `dorny/paths-filter@v3` step with filter `sdk`: `sdk-python/**`\n134: - [ ] T-009.04 Job `python-sdk-tests` on `ubuntu-latest`: step 1 — `actions/checkout@v4`\n135: - [ ] T-009.05 Job `python-sdk-tests`: step 2 — paths-filter step with id `filter`\n136: - [ ] T-009.06 Job `python-sdk-tests`: step 3 — `actions/setup-python@v5` with `python-version: '3.12'`, `working-directory: sdk-python`, conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.sdk == 'true'`\n137: - [ ] T-009.07 Job `python-sdk-tests`: step 4 — `run: pip install pytest`, `working-directory: sdk-python`, conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.sdk == 'true'`\n138: - [ ] T-009.08 Job `python-sdk-tests`: step 5 — `run: pip install -e .`, `working-directory: sdk-python`, conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.sdk == 'true'`\n139: - [ ] T-009.09 Job `python-sdk-tests`: step 6 — `run: python -m pytest tests/ -v`, `working-directory: sdk-python`, conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.sdk == 'true'`\n140: \n141: **验收**: `yq '.name' .github/workflows/python-sdk-tests.yml` → `Python SDK Tests`; `grep 'merge_group' .github/workflows/python-sdk-tests.yml` 有输出; `grep 'python-version.*3.12' .github/workflows/python-sdk-tests.yml` 有输出; `grep 'working-directory.*sdk-python' .github/workflows/python-sdk-tests.yml` 出现 ≥ 3 次; `grep 'pytest tests/' .github/workflows/python-sdk-tests.yml` 有输出; `grep 'pip install -e .' .github/workflows/python-sdk-tests.yml` 有输出\n142: \n143: ---\n144: \n145: ### T-010: python-lint.yml — Python Lint with Ruff\n146: \n147: - [ ] T-010.01 Create `.github/workflows/python-lint.yml` with `name: Python Lint`\n148: - [ ] T-010.02 Trigger: `pull_request` with branches `main`, `release-*`\n149: - [ ] T-010.03 Define `dorny/paths-filter@v3` step with filter `python`: `cmd/cli/**`, `sdk-python/**`, `example/**`, `test/**/*.py`, `pyproject.toml`, workflow self\n150: - [ ] T-010.04 Job `python_lint` on `ubuntu-latest`: step 1 — `actions/checkout@v4`\n151: - [ ] T-010.05 Job `python_lint`: step 2 — paths-filter step with id `filter`\n152: - [ ] T-010.06 Job `python_lint`: step 3 — `actions/setup-python@v5` with `python-version: '3.10'`, conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.python == 'true'`\n153: - [ ] T-010.07 Job `python_lint`: step 4 — `run: pip install ruff`, conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.python == 'true'`\n154: - [ ] T-010.08 Job `python_lint`: step 5 — `run: python3 -m ruff check . --config pyproject.toml`, conditional `if: steps.filter.outputs.python == 'true'`\n155: \n156: **验收**: `yq '.name' .github/workflows/python-lint.yml` → `Python Lint`; `grep 'python-version.*3.10' .github/workflows/python-lint.yml` 有输出; `grep 'ruff check' .github/workflows/python-lint.yml` 有输出; `grep 'pyproject.toml' .github/workflows/python-lint.yml` 有输出; `grep 'cmd/cli' .github/workflows/python-lint.yml` 有输出; `grep 'example/' .github/workflows/python-lint.yml` 有输出; `grep 'test/\\*\\*/\\*.py' .github/workflows/python-lint.yml` 有输出\n157: \n158: ---\n159: \n160: ## Phase 4: Release & Automation Workflows\n161: \n162: ### T-011: build-push-release.yml — Multi-arch Image Publication\n163: \n164: - [ ] T-011.01 Create `.github/workflows/build-push-release.yml` with `name: Build and Push Release Images`\n165: - [ ] T-011.02 Trigger: `push` with branches `main`, tags `v*.*.*`, `v*.*.*-*`\n166: - [ ] T-011.03 Job `build-and-push` on `ubuntu-latest`: step 1 — `actions/checkout@v3`\n167: - [ ] T-011.04 Job `build-and-push`: step 2 — `actions/setup-go@v4` with `go-version: '1.24.4'`\n168: - [ ] T-011.05 Job `build-and-push`: step 3 — `docker/setup-buildx-action@v2`\n169: - [ ] T-011.06 Job `build-and-push`: step 4 — `docker/login-action@v3` with `registry: ghcr.io`, `username: ${{ github.actor }}`, `password: ${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}`\n170: - [ ] T-011.07 Job `build-and-push`: step 5 — set `TAG` env: `latest` for branch push, `github.ref_name` for tag push\n171: - [ ] T-011.08 Job `build-and-push`: step 6 — set `IMAGE_REGISTRY` env to `ghcr.io/${{ github.repository_owner }}`\n172: - [ ] T-011.09 Job `build-and-push`: step 7 — `run: make docker-buildx-push` (workloadmanager) with env `IMAGE_REGISTRY`, `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_IMAGE=workloadmanager:${{ env.TAG }}`\n173: - [ ] T-011.10 Job `build-and-push`: step 8 — `run: make docker-buildx-push-router` with env `IMAGE_REGISTRY`, `ROUTER_IMAGE=router:${{ env.TAG }}`\n174: - [ ] T-011.11 Job `build-and-push`: step 9 — `run: make docker-buildx-push-picod` with env `IMAGE_REGISTRY`, `PICOD_IMAGE=picod:${{ env.TAG }}`\n175: \n176: **验收**: `yq '.name' .github/workflows/build-push-release.yml` → `Build and Push Release Images`; `grep 'push.*tags' .github/workflows/build-push-release.yml` 或等效 tag 触发配置存在; `grep 'docker/login-action' .github/workflows/build-push-release.yml` 有输出; `grep 'ghcr.io' .github/workflows/build-push-release.yml` 有输出; `grep 'docker-buildx-push' .github/workflows/build-push-release.yml` 出现 ≥ 3 次; `grep 'IMAGE_REGISTRY' .github/workflows/build-push-release.yml` 有输出; `grep 'TAG' .github/workflows/build-push-release.yml` 有输出; `grep 'go-version.*1.24.4' .github/workflows/build-push-release.yml` 有输出\n177: \n178: ---\n179: \n180: ### T-012: dify-plugin-publish.yml — Dify Plugin Packaging & PR\n181: \n182: - [ ] T-012.01 Create `.github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml` with `name: Dify Plugin Publish`\n183: - [ ] T-012.02 Trigger: `push` with tags `dify-plugin/v*`\n184: - [ ] T-012.03 Job `publish` on `ubuntu-latest`: step 1 — `actions/checkout@v4`\n185: - [ ] T-012.04 Job `publish`: step 2 — download `dify-plugin` CLI version `0.0.6`\n186: - [ ] T-012.05 Job `publish`: step 3 — install `yq`\n187: - [ ] T-012.06 Job `publish`: step 4 — read `manifest.yaml` to extract plugin name and version using `yq`\n188: - [ ] T-012.07 Job `publish`: step 5 — package plugin using `dify-plugin` CLI to produce `.difypkg` file\n189: - [ ] T-012.08 Job `publish`: step 6 — checkout `author/dify-plugins` repo using `PLUGIN_ACTION` secret for auth\n190: - [ ] T-012.09 Job `publish`: step 7 — move `.difypkg` to target repo, create branch, commit, push\n191: - [ ] T-012.10 Job `publish`: step 8 — `gh pr create` to `langgenius/dify-plugins` with `GH_TOKEN`\n192: \n193: **验收**: `yq '.name' .github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml` → `Dify Plugin Publish`; `grep 'dify-plugin/v' .github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml` 有输出; `grep 'dify-plugin' .github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml` 出现 ≥ 3 次; `grep 'yq' .github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml` 有输出; `grep 'manifest.yaml' .github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml` 有输出; `grep 'PLUGIN_ACTION' .github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml` 有输出; `grep 'dify-plugins' .github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml` 有输出; `grep 'gh pr create' .github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml` 或 `create-pull-request` 有输出; `grep '.difypkg' .github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml` 有输出\n194: \n195: ---\n196: \n197: ### T-013: workflows-approve.yml — Auto-approve for Repeat Contributors\n198: \n199: - [ ] T-013.01 Create `.github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml` with `name: Approve Workflows`\n200: - [ ] T-013.02 Trigger: `pull_request_target` with types `labeled`, `synchronize`, branches `main`, `release-**`\n201: - [ ] T-013.03 Job `approve` on `ubuntu-latest`: step 1 — `actions/checkout@v4`\n202: - [ ] T-013.04 Job `approve`: step 2 — `actions/github-script@v7` with inline JavaScript:\n203:   - Query GitHub API to list PRs by the PR author to the repository\n204:   - If PR count > 1 (repeat contributor) OR PR has `ok-to-test` label:\n205:     - List workflow runs for `head_sha` with `status: action_required`\n206:     - For each run: call `octokit.rest.actions.approveWorkflowRun()`\n207:   - Else: skip (first-time contributor without label)\n208: \n209: **验收**: `yq '.name' .github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml` → `Approve Workflows`; `grep 'pull_request_target' .github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml` 有输出; `grep 'labeled' .github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml` 有输出; `grep 'synchronize' .github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml` 有输出; `grep 'github-script' .github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml` 有输出; `grep 'ok-to-test' .github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml` 有输出; `grep 'action_required' .github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml` 有输出; `grep 'approveWorkflowRun' .github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml` 有输出\n210: \n211: ---\n212: \n213: ## Phase 5: Validation & Final Verification\n214: \n215: ### T-014: YAML syntax validation for all 12 workflows\n216: \n217: - [ ] T-014.01 Run `actionlint .github/workflows/main.yml` — exit code 0\n218: - [ ] T-014.02 Run `actionlint .github/workflows/lint.yml` — exit code 0\n219: - [ ] T-014.03 Run `actionlint .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml` — exit code 0\n220: - [ ] T-014.04 Run `actionlint .github/workflows/e2e.yml` — exit code 0\n221: - [ ] T-014.05 Run `actionlint .github/workflows/codegen-check.yml` — exit code 0\n222: - [ ] T-014.06 Run `actionlint .github/workflows/copyright-check.yml` — exit code 0\n223: - [ ] T-014.07 Run `actionlint .github/workflows/codespell.yml` — exit code 0\n224: - [ ] T-014.08 Run `actionlint .github/workflows/python-sdk-tests.yml` — exit code 0\n225: - [ ] T-014.09 Run `actionlint .github/workflows/python-lint.yml` — exit code 0\n226: - [ ] T-014.10 Run `actionlint .github/workflows/build-push-release.yml` — exit code 0\n227: - [ ] T-014.11 Run `actionlint .github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml` — exit code 0\n228: - [ ] T-014.12 Run `actionlint .github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml` — exit code 0\n229: \n230: **验收**: `actionlint .github/workflows/*.yml` 全部退出码 0；或 `find .github/workflows/ -name '*.yml' | xargs actionlint` 无错误输出\n231: \n232: ---\n233: \n234: ### T-015: Workflow count and directory structure verification\n235: \n236: - [ ] T-015.01 `.github/workflows/` 目录恰好包含 12 个 `.yml` 文件\n237: - [ ] T-015.02 文件名与 spec 一致：`main.yml`, `lint.yml`, `test-coverage.yml`, `e2e.yml`, `codegen-check.yml`, `copyright-check.yml`, `codespell.yml`, `python-sdk-tests.yml`, `python-lint.yml`, `build-push-release.yml`, `dify-plugin-publish.yml`, `workflows-approve.yml`\n238: - [ ] T-015.03 所有 workflow 的 `name` 字段与设计文档一致\n239: \n240: **验收**: `ls .github/workflows/*.yml | wc -l` → 12; `ls .github/workflows/` 输出 12 个指定文件名\n241: \n242: ---\n243: \n244: ### T-016: Path filter configuration verification\n245: \n246: - [ ] T-016.01 `lint.yml` filter `lint` 包含 `**/*.go`, `go.mod`, `go.sum`, `.golangci.yml`, `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n247: - [ ] T-016.02 `test-coverage.yml` filter `coverage` 包含 `**`, `!*.md`, `!*.svg`, `!*.png`\n248: - [ ] T-016.03 `codegen-check.yml` filter `codegen` 包含 `pkg/apis/**`, `hack/**`, `.github/workflows/**`, `Makefile`\n249: - [ ] T-016.04 `copyright-check.yml` filter `copyright` 包含 `**`, `!*.md`, `!*.svg`, `!*.png`, `!docs/**`, `!.github/**`\n250: - [ ] T-016.05 `python-sdk-tests.yml` filter `sdk` 包含 `sdk-python/**`\n251: - [ ] T-016.06 `python-lint.yml` filter `python` 包含 `cmd/cli/**`, `sdk-python/**`, `example/**`, `test/**/*.py`, `pyproject.toml`\n252: \n253: **验收**: 对每个 workflow 执行 `grep -A 10 'paths:' .github/workflows/<file>.yml` 验证路径模式与 spec 一致\n254: \n255: ---\n256: \n257: ### T-017: Go/Python version matrix verification\n258: \n259: - [ ] T-017.01 `lint.yml` 使用 Go `1.24`\n260: - [ ] T-017.02 `test-coverage.yml` 使用 Go `1.24`\n261: - [ ] T-017.03 `e2e.yml` 使用 Go `1.23`\n262: - [ ] T-017.04 `codegen-check.yml` 使用 Go `1.24.4`\n263: - [ ] T-017.05 `build-push-release.yml` 使用 Go `1.24.4`\n264: - [ ] T-017.06 `python-sdk-tests.yml` 使用 Python `3.12`\n265: - [ ] T-017.07 `python-lint.yml` 使用 Python `3.10`\n266: \n267: **验收**: `grep -r 'go-version' .github/workflows/ | sort`; `grep -r 'python-version' .github/workflows/ | sort` — 输出与上表一致\n268: \n269: ---\n270: \n271: ### T-018: Secret and env variable verification\n272: \n273: - [ ] T-018.01 `test-coverage.yml` 声明 `workflow_call` 中 `CODECOV_TOKEN` 为 `required: false`\n274: - [ ] T-018.02 `test-coverage.yml` Codecov 步骤使用 `if: ${{ secrets.CODECOV_TOKEN != '' }}` 条件\n275: - [ ] T-018.03 `build-push-release.yml` 使用 `secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN` 登录 GHCR\n276: - [ ] T-018.04 `dify-plugin-publish.yml` 使用 `secrets.PLUGIN_ACTION` 进行跨仓库操作\n277: - [ ] T-018.05 `e2e.yml` 设置 `ARTIFACTS_PATH=${{ github.workspace }}/e2e-logs`\n278: - [ ] T-018.06 `build-push-release.yml` 设置 `IMAGE_REGISTRY=ghcr.io/${{ github.repository_owner }}`\n279: \n280: **验收**: `grep 'CODECOV_TOKEN' .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml` 出现 ≥ 2 次; `grep 'PLUGIN_ACTION' .github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml` 有输出; `grep 'ARTIFACTS_PATH' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` 有输出; `grep 'IMAGE_REGISTRY' .github/workflows/build-push-release.yml` 有输出\n281: \n282: ---\n283: \n284: ### T-019: Cleanup and always() step verification\n285: \n286: - [ ] T-019.01 `e2e.yml` 包含 `make e2e-clean` 步骤且条件为 `if: always()`\n287: - [ ] T-019.02 `codespell.yml` 包含文件恢复步骤且条件为 `if: always()`\n288: - [ ] T-019.03 `e2e.yml` 包含 `if: failure()` 条件的日志上传步骤\n289: \n290: **验收**: `grep -B1 'make e2e-clean' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` 含 `if: always()`; `grep -B1 'restore' .github/workflows/codespell.yml` 或等效恢复步骤含 `if: always()`; `grep 'if: failure()' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` 有输出\n291: \n292: ---\n293: \n294: ### T-020: Trigger matrix cross-validation\n295: \n296: - [ ] T-020.01 PR 到 `main` 应触发的 9 个 workflow 均配置了 `pull_request` → `main`: `main.yml`, `lint.yml`, `test-coverage.yml`, `e2e.yml`, `codegen-check.yml`, `copyright-check.yml`, `codespell.yml`, `python-sdk-tests.yml`, `python-lint.yml`\n297: - [ ] T-020.02 PR 到 `release-*` 应触发的 8 个 workflow 均配置了 `pull_request` → `release-*`: `main.yml`, `lint.yml`, `e2e.yml`, `codegen-check.yml`, `copyright-check.yml`, `codespell.yml`, `python-lint.yml`, `workflows-approve.yml`（注：`test-coverage.yml` 仅 PR to main, `python-sdk-tests.yml` 无分支限制）\n298: - [ ] T-020.03 `build-push-release.yml` 仅响应 `push` → `main` 和 tags `v*.*.*`/`v*.*.*-*`\n299: - [ ] T-020.04 `dify-plugin-publish.yml` 仅响应 `push` tags `dify-plugin/v*`\n300: - [ ] T-020.05 `workflows-approve.yml` 使用 `pull_request_target` types `labeled`, `synchronize`\n301: \n302: **验收**: `grep -l 'pull_request' .github/workflows/*.yml` 包含预期的 9+ 个文件; `grep -l 'push' .github/workflows/*.yml` 包含 `build-push-release.yml` 和 `dify-plugin-publish.yml`; `grep 'pull_request_target' .github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml` 有输出\n303: \n304: ---\n305: \n306: ## Dependency Graph\n307: \n308: ```\n309: T-001 (create .github/workflows/) ──┬── T-002 (main.yml)\n310:                                      ├── T-003 (lint.yml)\n311:                                      ├── T-004 (test-coverage.yml)\n312:                                      ├── T-005 (e2e.yml)\n313:                                      ├── T-006 (codegen-check.yml)\n314:                                      ├── T-007 (copyright-check.yml)\n315:                                      ├── T-008 (codespell.yml)\n316:                                      ├── T-009 (python-sdk-tests.yml)\n317:                                      ├── T-010 (python-lint.yml)\n318:                                      ├── T-011 (build-push-release.yml)\n319:                                      ├── T-012 (dify-plugin-publish.yml)\n320:                                      └── T-013 (workflows-approve.yml)\n321:                                                                         │\n322: T-002 ── T-003 ── T-004 ── T-005 ──┤\n323: T-006 ── T-007 ── T-008 ───────────┤\n324: T-009 ── T-010 ────────────────────┤                                   ├── T-014 (actionlint all)\n325: T-011 ── T-012 ── T-013 ───────────┤                                   ├── T-015 (count & structure)\n326:                                     │                                   ├── T-016 (path filters)\n327:                                     │                                   ├── T-017 (version matrix)\n328:                                     │                                   ├── T-018 (secrets/env)\n329:                                     │                                   ├── T-019 (cleanup/always)\n330:                                     │                                   └── T-020 (trigger matrix)\n331: ```\n332: \n333: ## Parallelizable Groups\n334: \n335: | Group | Tasks | Prerequisites |\n336: |-------|-------|---------------|\n337: | G1 | T-001 (create directory) | None |\n338: | G2 | T-002 (main.yml), T-003 (lint.yml), T-004 (test-coverage.yml), T-005 (e2e.yml), T-006 (codegen-check.yml), T-007 (copyright-check.yml), T-008 (codespell.yml), T-009 (python-sdk-tests.yml), T-010 (python-lint.yml), T-011 (build-push-release.yml), T-012 (dify-plugin-publish.yml), T-013 (workflows-approve.yml) | G1 |\n339: | G3 | T-014 (actionlint), T-015 (count), T-016 (path filters), T-017 (versions), T-018 (secrets), T-019 (cleanup), T-020 (triggers) | G2 |\n340: \n341: ---\n342: \n343: ## Acceptance Criteria\n344: \n345: | # | Criterion | Command |\n346: |---|-----------|---------|\n347: | AC1 | `.github/workflows/` 目录存在且含 12 个 `.yml` 文件 | `ls .github/workflows/*.yml \\| wc -l` → 12 |\n348: | AC2 | 所有 12 个 workflow 文件通过 actionlint 语法检查 | `actionlint .github/workflows/*.yml` 退出码 0 |\n349: | AC3 | main.yml 配置 PR 触发 Docker 构建 | `grep 'make docker-build' .github/workflows/main.yml` 且 `grep 'pull_request' .github/workflows/main.yml` |\n350: | AC4 | lint.yml 使用 paths-filter + Go 1.24 + make lint | `grep 'paths-filter' .github/workflows/lint.yml` && `grep 'go-version.*1.24' .github/workflows/lint.yml` && `grep 'make lint' .github/workflows/lint.yml` |\n351: | AC5 | test-coverage.yml 支持 workflow_call + race coverage + Codecov | `grep 'workflow_call' .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml` && `grep '\\-race' .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml` && `grep 'codecov-action' .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml` |\n352: | AC6 | e2e.yml 使用 Kind v0.30.0 install_only + ARTIFACTS_PATH + cleanup | `grep 'kind-action' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` && `grep 'install_only' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` && `grep 'ARTIFACTS_PATH' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` && `grep 'e2e-clean' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` |\n353: | AC7 | codegen-check.yml 使用 Go 1.24.4 + make gen-check | `grep 'go-version.*1.24.4' .github/workflows/codegen-check.yml` && `grep 'make gen-check' .github/workflows/codegen-check.yml` |\n354: | AC8 | copyright-check.yml 安装 moreutils + make gen-copyright + git diff | `grep 'moreutils' .github/workflows/copyright-check.yml` && `grep 'make gen-copyright' .github/workflows/copyright-check.yml` && `grep 'git diff --exit-code' .github/workflows/copyright-check.yml` |\n355: | AC9 | codespell.yml 临时移开 false-positive 文件 + restore on always | `grep 'pyproject.toml' .github/workflows/codespell.yml` && `grep 'if: always()' .github/workflows/codespell.yml` |\n356: | AC10 | python-sdk-tests.yml 使用 Python 3.12 + pytest in sdk-python | `grep 'python-version.*3.12' .github/workflows/python-sdk-tests.yml` && `grep 'pytest' .github/workflows/python-sdk-tests.yml` && `grep 'sdk-python' .github/workflows/python-sdk-tests.yml` |\n357: | AC11 | python-lint.yml 使用 Python 3.10 + ruff check | `grep 'python-version.*3.10' .github/workflows/python-lint.yml` && `grep 'ruff check' .github/workflows/python-lint.yml` |\n358: | AC12 | build-push-release.yml 登录 GHCR + 推送 3 个镜像 | `grep 'docker/login-action' .github/workflows/build-push-release.yml` && `grep 'docker-buildx-push' .github/workflows/build-push-release.yml` 出现 ≥ 3 次 |\n359: | AC13 | dify-plugin-publish.yml 打包插件 + 创建 PR 到 langgenius/dify-plugins | `grep 'dify-plugin' .github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml` && `grep 'dify-plugins' .github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml` |\n360: | AC14 | workflows-approve.yml 使用 pull_request_target + github-script + approveWorkflowRun | `grep 'pull_request_target' .github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml` && `grep 'github-script' .github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml` && `grep 'approveWorkflowRun' .github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml` |\n361: | AC15 | 6 个 workflow 使用 dorny/paths-filter@v3 进行路径过滤 | `grep -l 'dorny/paths-filter' .github/workflows/*.yml \\| wc -l` → 6 |\n362: | AC16 | CODECOV_TOKEN 为可选 secret（workflow_call required: false + conditional upload） | `grep -A2 'CODECOV_TOKEN' .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml \\| grep 'required: false'` && `grep \"secrets.CODECOV_TOKEN != ''\" .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml` |\n363: | AC17 | e2e.yml 使用 ubuntu-24.04 runner | `grep 'ubuntu-24.04' .github/workflows/e2e.yml` |\n364: | AC18 | 所有 workflow 名称与设计文档一致 | `for f in .github/workflows/*.yml; do echo \"$f: $(yq '.name' $f)\"; done` 输出 12 个正确名称 |\n\n(End of file - total 364 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-034 — CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows) — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** .github\n> **Language:** YAML\n> **Size:** L\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-034/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-034/design.md`, `changes/AR-034/delta-spec.md`\n> **Dependency:** AR-033 (Makefile targets), AR-032 (Dockerfiles)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Infrastructure Workflows (PR Gate)\n\n### T-001: Create `.github/workflows/` directory structure\n\n- [ ] T-001.01 Create `.github/workflows/` directory\n\n**验收**: `ls -d .github/workflows/` 目录存在\n\n---","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-034/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775883012251,"end":1775883012275}}}}
