{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775883180889,"sessionID":"ses_2851ffec2ffeiksYiHePqod4EM","part":{"id":"prt_d7ae0789b001E3lFC5t3Qx2Vs4","messageID":"msg_d7ae06d9f001wGbwUSL6vM3ua4","sessionID":"ses_2851ffec2ffeiksYiHePqod4EM","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_9c2b83e66ab24ef496cc8720","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-036 — Dify 插件集成 — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** integrations\n> **Language:** Python\n> **Size:** M\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-036/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-036/design.md`, `changes/AR-036/delta-spec.md`\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Dify Plugin Bootstrap & Manifest\n\n### T-001: Create plugin directory structure\n\n- [ ] T-001.01 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/` directory\n- [ ] T-001.02 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/provider/` subdirectory\n- [ ] T-001.03 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/tools/` subdirectory\n\n**验收**: `ls -d integrations/dify-plugin/provider/ integrations/dify-plugin/tools/` 两个子目录均存在\n\n---\n\n### T-002: Create `main.py` plugin entrypoint\n\n- [ ] T-002.01 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/main.py`\n- [ ] T-002.02 Import `Plugin` and `DifyPluginEnv` from `dify_plugin`\n- [ ] T-002.03 Execute `Plugin(DifyPluginEnv(MAX_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=120)).run()` at module level\n\n**验收**: `grep 'MAX_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=120' integrations/dify-plugin/main.py` 有输出; `grep 'Plugin(DifyPluginEnv' integrations/dify-plugin/main.py` 有输出\n\n---\n\n### T-003: Create `manifest.yaml` root plugin manifest\n\n- [ ] T-003.01 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/manifest.yaml`\n- [ ] T-003.02 Set top-level identity: `version: \"0.0.2\"`, `type: \"plugin\"`, `author: \"volcano-sh\"`, `name: \"agentcube\"`\n- [ ] T-003.03 Set `label` map with `en_US`, `ja_JP`, `zh_Hans`, `pt_BR` all → `\"Agentcube\"`\n- [ ] T-003.04 Set `description` as multilingual map with localized AgentCube descriptions\n- [ ] T-003.05 Set `icon: \"icon.png\"` and `icon_dark: \"icon-dark.png\"`\n- [ ] T-003.06 Set `resource` with `memory` and `permission` subtree (flags and sizes for `tool`, `model`, `endpoint`, `app`, `storage`)\n- [ ] T-003.07 Set `plugins.tools: [provider/agentcube.yaml]`\n- [ ] T-003.08 Set `meta` with `version`, `arch: [amd64, arm64]`, `runner` (`language: \"python\"`, `version: \"3.12\"`, `entrypoint: \"main\"`), `minimum_dify_version: null`\n- [ ] T-003.09 Set `created_at`, `privacy`, `repo`, `verified` fields\n\n**验收**: `python3 -c \"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('integrations/dify-plugin/manifest.yaml')); assert d['version']=='0.0.2'; assert d['type']=='plugin'; assert d['author']=='volcano-sh'; assert d['name']=='agentcube'; assert d['meta']['runner']['language']=='python'; assert d['plugins.tools']==['provider/agentcube.yaml']\"` 退出码 0\n\n---\n\n### T-004: Create `requirements.txt` for plugin dependencies\n\n- [ ] T-004.01 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/requirements.txt`\n- [ ] T-004.02 Pin `dify-plugin>=0.4.2,<0.5.0`\n- [ ] T-004.03 Pin `agentcube-sdk>=0.0.10`\n\n**验收**: `grep 'dify-plugin>=0.4.2,<0.5.0' integrations/dify-plugin/requirements.txt` 有输出; `grep 'agentcube-sdk>=0.0.10' integrations/dify-plugin/requirements.txt` 有输出\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Provider Descriptor & Implementation\n\n### T-005: Create `provider/agentcube.yaml` tool provider descriptor\n\n- [ ] T-005.01 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.yaml`\n- [ ] T-005.02 Define `identity` with `author`, `name`, multilingual `label`, multilingual `description`, and `icon`\n- [ ] T-005.03 Include commented-out `oauth_schema` block (present as YAML comments only)\n- [ ] T-005.04 Set `tools: [tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml]`\n- [ ] T-005.05 Set `extra.python.source: \"provider/agentcube.py\"`\n\n**验收**: `python3 -c \"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.yaml')); assert 'identity' in d; assert d['tools']==['tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml']; assert d['extra']['python']['source']=='provider/agentcube.py'\"` 退出码 0; `grep '#.*oauth_schema' integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.yaml` 有输出（注释形式存在）\n\n---\n\n### T-006: Create `provider/agentcube.py` provider implementation\n\n- [ ] T-006.01 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.py`\n- [ ] T-006.02 Import `ToolProvider` from `dify_plugin`\n- [ ] T-006.03 Import `ToolProviderCredentialValidationError` from `dify_plugin.errors.tool`\n- [ ] T-006.04 Define `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider(ToolProvider)` class\n- [ ] T-006.05 Implement `_validate_credentials(self, credentials: dict[str, Any]) -> None` with try/except that raises `ToolProviderCredentialValidationError(str(e))` on failure\n- [ ] T-006.06 Successful validation returns `None` without raising\n\n**验收**: `python3 -c \"\nimport ast, sys\ntree = ast.parse(open('integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.py').read())\nclasses = [n for n in ast.walk(tree) if isinstance(n, ast.ClassDef)]\nassert any(n.name == 'AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider' for n in classes), 'Class not found'\nmethods = [n for c in classes if c.name == 'AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider' for n in ast.walk(c) if isinstance(n, ast.FunctionDef) and n.name == '_validate_credentials']\nassert len(methods) == 1, '_validate_credentials not found'\n\" ` 退出码 0; `grep 'ToolProviderCredentialValidationError' integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.py` 有输出\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: Tool Schema & Implementation\n\n### T-007: Create `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml` tool schema\n\n- [ ] T-007.01 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml`\n- [ ] T-007.02 Define `identity` with `name: \"agentcube-code-interpreter\"`, `author: \"agentcube\"`, multilingual `label`/`description` (human + llm)\n- [ ] T-007.03 Define required parameter `router_url` (type: string, required: true, form: form)\n- [ ] T-007.04 Define required parameter `workload_manager_url` (type: string, required: true, form: form)\n- [ ] T-007.05 Define optional parameter `language` (type: select, required: false, form: llm, options: `[python, javascript, typescript]`)\n- [ ] T-007.06 Define optional parameters: `code` (string), `command` (string), `session_id` (string), `session_reuse` (boolean), `code_interpreter_id` (string), all with `required: false`, `form: llm`\n- [ ] T-007.07 Each parameter includes `name`, `type`, `required`, `label`, `human_description`, `llm_description`, `form`\n- [ ] T-007.08 Set `extra.python.source: \"tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py\"`\n\n**验收**: `python3 -c \"\nimport yaml\nd = yaml.safe_load(open('integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml'))\nassert d['identity']['name'] == 'agentcube-code-interpreter'\nparams = {p['name']: p for p in d['parameters']}\nassert params['router_url']['required'] == True\nassert params['workload_manager_url']['required'] == True\nassert params['language']['type'] == 'select'\nassert set(params['language']['options']) == {'python', 'javascript', 'typescript'}\nassert params['session_reuse']['type'] == 'boolean'\nassert d['extra']['python']['source'] == 'tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py'\n\"` 退出码 0\n\n---\n\n### T-008: Create `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py` tool implementation\n\n- [ ] T-008.01 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py`\n- [ ] T-008.02 Import `Tool` from `dify_plugin`, `ToolInvokeMessage` from `dify_plugin.entities.tool`, `CodeInterpreterClient` from `agentcube`\n- [ ] T-008.03 Import `Generator` from `collections.abc` and `Any` from `typing`\n- [ ] T-008.04 Define `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterTool(Tool)` class\n- [ ] T-008.05 Implement `_invoke(self, tool_parameters: dict[str, Any]) -> Generator[ToolInvokeMessage]` that calls `self.execute(**tool_parameters)` and yields `self.create_json_message(result)`\n- [ ] T-008.06 Implement `execute` with parameters: `router_url`, `workload_manager_url`, `language=\"python\"`, `code_interpreter_id`, `session_id`, `code`, `command`, `session_reuse=False`, `**kwargs`\n- [ ] T-008.07 `execute` delegates to `CodeInterpret