 T-017 (Dify tests), T-018 (PCAP tests) | G4 (T-006, T-008), G7 (T-011, T-012, T-013) |\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n| # | Criterion | Command |\n|---|-----------|---------|\n| AC1 | Plugin directory structure exists with provider/ and tools/ subdirs | `ls -d integrations/dify-plugin/provider/ integrations/dify-plugin/tools/` 退出码 0 |\n| AC2 | `main.py` runs plugin with `MAX_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=120` | `grep 'MAX_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=120' integrations/dify-plugin/main.py` 有输出 |\n| AC3 | `manifest.yaml` has correct version, type, author, name, meta.runner | `python3 -c \"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('integrations/dify-plugin/manifest.yaml')); assert d['version']=='0.0.2' and d['type']=='plugin' and d['meta']['runner']['language']=='python'\"` 退出码 0 |\n| AC4 | Plugin requirements pin dify-plugin and agentcube-sdk | `grep 'dify-plugin>=0.4.2,<0.5.0' integrations/dify-plugin/requirements.txt` && `grep 'agentcube-sdk>=0.0.10' integrations/dify-plugin/requirements.txt` |\n| AC5 | Provider descriptor has identity, tools list, python source | `python3 -c \"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.yaml')); assert d['extra']['python']['source']=='provider/agentcube.py'\"` 退出码 0 |\n| AC6 | Provider class inherits ToolProvider with _validate_credentials | `grep 'class AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider(ToolProvider)' integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.py` 有输出 |\n| AC7 | Tool schema has required router_url/workload_manager_url and optional language select | `python3 -c \"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml')); params={p['name']:p for p in d['parameters']}; assert params['router_url']['required'] and params['language']['type']=='select'\"` 退出码 0 |\n| AC8 | Tool class inherits Tool with _invoke and execute methods | `python3 -c \"import ast; tree=ast.parse(open('integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py').read()); classes=[n for n in ast.walk(tree) if isinstance(n,ast.ClassDef)]; assert any(n.name=='AgentcubeCodeInterpreterTool' for n in classes)\"` 退出码 0 |\n| AC9 | Plugin docs exist (GUIDE.md, README.md, PRIVACY.md, .difyignore) | `ls integrations/dify-plugin/GUIDE.md integrations/dify-plugin/README.md integrations/dify-plugin/PRIVACY.md integrations/dify-plugin/.difyignore` 均存在 |\n| AC10 | PCAP analyzer requirements pinned, agentcube NOT listed | `grep 'fastapi==0.120.0' example/pcap-analyzer/requirements.txt` 有输出; `grep 'agentcube' example/pcap-analyzer/requirements.txt` 无输出 |\n| AC11 | `pcap_analyzer.py` has SandboxRunner, agent builders, orchestration, FastAPI app | `python3 -c \"import ast; tree=ast.parse(open('example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py').read()); names=[n.name for n in ast.walk(tree) if isinstance(n,(ast.ClassDef,ast.FunctionDef,ast.AsyncFunctionDef))]; assert 'SandboxRunner' in names and 'build_react_agent' in names and 'analyze_endpoint' in names\"` 退出码 0 |\n| AC12 | Dockerfile uses uv base, vendors agentcube, exposes 8000 | `grep 'ghcr.io/astral-sh/uv:python3.12-bookworm-slim' example/pcap-analyzer/Dockerfile` && `grep 'sdk-python/agentcube' example/pcap-analyzer/Dockerfile` && `grep 'EXPOSE 8000' example/pcap-analyzer/Dockerfile` |\n| AC13 | K8s Deployment has correct image, resources, env, command | `python3 -c \"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('example/pcap-analyzer/deployment.yaml')); c=d['spec']['template']['spec']['containers'][0]; assert c['image']=='pcap-analyzer:latest' and c['command']==['uv'] and c['args']==['run','pcap_analyzer.py']\"` 退出码 0 |\n| AC14 | Dify plugin tests exist (test_provider.py, test_tool.py, test_manifest.py) | `ls integrations/dify-plugin/tests/test_provider.py integrations/dify-plugin/tests/test_tool.py integrations/dify-plugin/tests/test_manifest.py` 均存在 |\n| AC15 | PCAP analyzer tests exist (test_pcap_analyzer.py, test_sandbox_runner.py, test_agents.py) | `ls example/pcap-analyzer/tests/test_pcap_analyzer.py example/pcap-analyzer/tests/test_sandbox_runner.py example/pcap-analyzer/tests/test_agents.py` 均存在 |\n| AC16 | AnalyzeResponse model has script, results, report fields | `grep 'class AnalyzeResponse' example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py` 有输出; `grep 'script: str' example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py` 有输出; `grep 'report: str' example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py` 有输出 |\n| AC17 | Startup validates OPENAI_API_KEY and fails if missing | `grep 'OPENAI_API_KEY' example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py` 出现 ≥ 2 次; `grep 'on_startup' example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py` 有输出 |\n| AC18 | All 16 files from delta-spec File Changes table are created | `for f in integrations/dify-plugin/main.py integrations/dify-plugin/manifest.yaml integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.yaml integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.py integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py integrations/dify-plugin/requirements.txt integrations/dify-plugin/GUIDE.md integrations/dify-plugin/README.md integrations/dify-plugin/PRIVACY.md integrations/dify-plugin/.difyignore example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py example/pcap-analyzer/requirements.txt example/pcap-analyzer/Dockerfile example/pcap-analyzer/deployment.yaml example/pcap-analyzer/README.md; do test -f \"$f\" || echo \"MISSING: $f\"; done` 无 MISSING 输出 |\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-036/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-036/tasks.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-036/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775883180865,"end":1775883180886}}}}
